data.description: Welcome to the ideal family home located on Lawton's sought-after east side! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. Situated in close proximity to MacArthur schools, it provides an excellent education hub for your children. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully updated interior, featuring granite countertops, modern cabinetry, a convenient kitchen island, and exquisite tile hardwood flooring. The bedrooms are adorned with  carpeting for added comfort. Outside, you'll find a covered patio, perfect for al fresco dining, overlooking a generous backyard with ample space for outdoor activities and a handy storage shed. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home offers both privacy and a sense of community. Don't miss your chance to call this charming property your own!  Call the Wright Team today for your private tour at 580-232-4321!
